    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold as-is and is best suited for a dedicated project or as a parts donor. The exterior shows significant wear, including several deep scratches, noticeable dents on the passenger side, and clear coat failure on the hood and roof. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with some tearing on the driver's seat, and the electronics are inconsistent. Mechanically, the engine runs but suffers from a persistent oil leak and a rough idle; the transmission also shifts harshly between second and third gear. While it still starts, it will require substantial mechanical work and cosmetic restoration to be roadworthy and reliable again.",
      "price": 3500.0,
